15 Sec. 2. 6 V.S.A. § 1105c is amended to read:
16 § 1105c. NEONICOTINOID PESTICIDES; PROHIBITED USES
17 (a) The following uses of neonicotinoid pesticides are prohibited:
18 (1) the outdoor application of neonicotinoid pesticides to any crop
19 during bloom;
